Package: po-diff
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3
Description: Tool for comparing gettext PO translation files
 po-diff is a command-line tool for comparing gettext PO translation
 files. It shows added, removed, and changed translations with
 context-aware diffing, making it useful for translation reviewers
 and maintainers.
 .
 Features include tracking fuzzy flag changes and multiple output
 formats (text, JSON, HTML).
